<h3 id="toc7"><span>Hormress版头</span></h3>
<hr />



<div class="module-body lang-cn">
<div class="lang-cn">
<div class="left-bar">
<div class="text-1">
<p>项目编号</p>
</div>
<div class="text-2">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">SCP-CN-001</span></p>
</div>
<div class="text-3">
<p>项目等级</p>
</div>
<div class="text-4">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">Principalis</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="right-bar">
<div class="clearance">
<div class="clear-6">
<div class="bar-1"></div>
<div class="bar-2"></div>
<div class="bar-3"></div>
<div class="bar-4"></div>
<div class="bar-5"></div>
<div class="bar-6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="right-text level-6 special-yes">
<div class="text-1 special-no">
<p>6级</p>
</div>
<div class="text-1 special-yes">
<p>6/CN-001级</p>
</div>
<div class="text-2"></div>
<div class="text-3">
<p>指派站点</p>
</div>
<div class="text-4">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">Area-CN-01</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lang-tr">
<div class="left-bar">
<div class="text-1">
<p>項目編號</p>
</div>
<div class="text-2">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">SCP-CN-001</span></p>
</div>
<div class="text-3">
<p>項目等級</p>
</div>
<div class="text-4">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">Principalis</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="right-bar">
<div class="clearance">
<div class="clear-6">
<div class="bar-1"></div>
<div class="bar-2"></div>
<div class="bar-3"></div>
<div class="bar-4"></div>
<div class="bar-5"></div>
<div class="bar-6"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="right-text level-6 special-yes">
<div class="text-1 special-no">
<p>6級</p>
</div>
<div class="text-1 special-yes">
<p>6/CN-001級</p>
</div>
<div class="text-2"></div>
<div class="text-3">
<p>指派站點</p>
</div>
<div class="text-4">
<p><span style="font-size:125%;">Area-CN-01</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<hr />
<p>一个可以说是池沼的版头格式，如果真的想用可以试试。</p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:module:hormress-head</span><br />
|lang=语言模式，填写cn或tr。<br />
|item-number=编号，格式如“CN-001”。<br />
|item-class=项目等级<br />
|clearance=机密等级（1到6）<br />
|special-clearance=机密模式，填写yes或no。填写yes时机密会显示成类似“6/CN-001级”的样式<br />
|item-site=指派站点<br />
]]</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<h3 id="toc8"><span>Hormress版头-暗色调</span></h3>
<hr />
<blockquote>
<p>没有示例，因为不能与普通色调版头同时使用。可以看看我的沙盒页<a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/draft:scp-cn-001-dr-hormress">的使用情况</a>。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>比上面的可能稍微好看一点，除了include网址之外使用方法相同。</p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:module:hormress-head-dark</span><br />
|lang=语言模式，填写cn或tr。<br />
|item-number=编号，格式如“CN-001”。<br />
|item-class=项目等级<br />
|clearance=机密等级（1到6）<br />
|special-clearance=机密模式，填写yes或no。填写yes时机密会显示成类似“6/CN-001级”的样式<br />
|item-site=指派站点<br />
]]</p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<h2 id="toc9"><span>简易CSS版式</span></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>注意CSS版式无法在这个页面上提供示例，<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">我也懒得截图，</span>可以在自己的沙盒页上试用。对效果不保证。可能会提供示例页面。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>注意</strong>：有部分版式可能影响到沙盒编辑，一些版式隐藏了编辑按钮，安全编辑请在网址后添加/norender/true再点击编辑。例如scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/dr-hormress这一页面的安全编辑网址是scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/dr-hormress/norender/true。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
