<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc19"><span><strong>Wanderers 版式</strong></span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/component:wanderers">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/component:wanderers</a></p>
<p>使用以下代码来引用这一版式：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:component:wanderers]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p>这个版式侧边栏显示有点问题。<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc20"><span>“终端”主题版式</span></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>基于Nu-SCP、模拟电脑终端制作的版式，注意这会隐藏侧栏和底部选项卡。颜色可用变量调整。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc21"><span><strong>终端</strong></span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>[[include :ah-sandbox:terminal]]</p>
</blockquote>
<p>可以加入下方模块进行调整：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[module&#32;css]]</span><br />
@import url(<a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal/code/1">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal/code/1</a>);</p>
<p>:root {<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;--color-bg:&#32;#002400;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;--color-mn:&#32;lightgreen;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;--color-bd:&#32;#227722;</span><br />
}<br />
[[/module]]</p>
</blockquote>
<p>三个颜色分别是页面背景颜色、主颜色（文字与部分元素边框）、页面边框颜色。<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc22"><span>超形上学部终端</span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal-pata">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal-pata</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:terminal-pata]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc23"><span>暗黑终端</span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal-black">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/terminal-black</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:terminal-black]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc24"><span>“普通”主题版式</span></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Hormress创作的、部分版头灵感来源于Nu-SCP版式的Sigma-9增补版式。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc25"><span><strong>Norm</strong></span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:cmr:norm]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p>此版式的核心，已经设置变量颜色。<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc26"><span><strong>Norm - “黑夜无疆”</strong></span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm:tnttb">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm:tnttb</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:ah-sandbox:cmr:norm:tnttb]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
