<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc27"><span><strong>Norm - 超形上学部</strong></span></h3>
<p><a href="http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm:pata">http://ah-sandbox.wikidot.com/cmr:norm:pata</a></p>
